metadata.name: " GENE_SIS "
metadata.description:
GENE_SIS Foundation_Bidding_War (One time event)

GENE_SIS is a 10k generative artwork project being produced by GHARLIERA.

“FOUNDATION means a lot to me. I started my career as a NFT artist on FND and it gave me a chance to meet everyone while creating what I wanted to create.
I would like to commence the grand beginning of GENE_SIS here with everyone.” -GHARLIERA

RULES

Time: 12:00 EST / Feb 23rd 2022
Listing price: 0.5 ETH
All bidders receive 1 Mintlist (multiple biddings will only grant you 1)
The winner will receive a free mint, equivalent to the number of total bids divided by 10 rounded off.
The winner will be able to participate in the GENE_SIS collection to submit a design idea for a rare trait.
The winning bid privileges will be granted as long as the artwork is not transferred or sold to a different wallet.
